data.name: txtLicence.Text
data.value:
=========== Eurobattle.net - World's Largest Warcarft III Community ===========
Eurobattle.net Forum @ http://eurobattle.net/
What is PvPGN Server? PvPGN (Player vs Player Gaming Network) is a free and open source software project offering emulation of various gaming network servers.
NOTE:
You must have Warcarft III: The Frozen Throne with patch 1.26a installed on your PC before running this installer, otherwise, no connection to Eurobattle.net can be made. This loader is specifically designed for Warcraft III: The Frozen Throne patch 1.26a. This software patches Warcraft III to enable connections to PvPGN Eurobattle.net servers. This program is Free Software distributed under the GNU GPL, version 3. For the full terms of the license refer to license.txt.
Using: Run 'euroloader.exe' to run Warcraft III : The Frozen Throne and play on Eurobattle.net PvPGN Server.
Rules: Sharing any kind of warez, cracks, serial numbers or illegal software will lead to immediate ban from Eurobattle.net. Publicly posting links to porn websites or any censored materials will lead to immediate ban from Eurobattle.net. Eurobattle.net may collect information about user's computer and any other necessary information in order to prevent the user from connecting to Eurobattle.net server; for example, but not exclusively, if in conflict with this EULA, or the server rules or the forum rules.
Credits:
Thanks to the PvPGN and bnetd contributors, and to Blizzard for making such a fantastic game. Thanks to Keres on the PvPGN forums for releasing fixes and updates, and to all who helped test and debug this release there.
Eurobattle.net Forum @ http://eurobattle.net/ PvPGN forums @ http://pelish.spfree.net/
Not for programmers :
If you are willing to help pvpgn development please check :
http://pelish.spfree.net/ and join their forums :)
Every help is welcome !.
Let's keep this project alive and burning !

data.value:
This version of the Euroloader was created by MusicDemon from Intcon. In order of Eurobattle.net's administrator Cen.
Euroloader is an open-source C#.NetV4.0 Forms Application and uses an API on a custom version of W3L.
